íŸ@91e9fb46ef9952001c53827e26a6f2bfb86669d58a0ed097fd3e4f81226fdc00⁄˙Title: This week in Nu #75
Path: Docs
Content:
ibraheemdev added the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/86] command reference to the book
richardpark-msft fixed a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/87] typo in the documentation
jonathandturner refreshed the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/91] command reference with the latest docs
, added a new 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2971] animated gif showing off Nushell
íŸ@d6065eed2a5edaf7a2ae330e0468e82263f74d678db1451ff5f2136547c25d15⁄'Title: This week in Nu #75
Path: Code
Content:
jonathandturner added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2962] rest support to blocks
, added erroring on 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2964] bad rows in column paths
, fixed a bug in the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2967] units of 
``ps``
 and 
``sys``
, released 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2974] 0.26.0
fdncred fixed the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2963] signature for the 
``char``
 command
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2973] multi-byte support for padding
, added more 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2975] modulo operations
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2976] pow operator
, allowed more 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2977] types to be converted to strings
andrasio improve 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2965] internal implementations for 
``str``
 commands
LhKipp added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2966] support for optional parameters and switches to the parser
JosephTLyons improved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2969] some of our test assertions
, removed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2970] unnecessary clones
